        public EmptyTask exportDmsTask

      • startExport

        public boolean startExport(Process process,
                           URI inZielVerzeichnis,
                           ExportDmsTask exportDmsTask)
        The function startExport() performs a DMS export to a desired place. In addition, it accepts an optional ExportDmsTask object. If that is passed in, the progress in it will be updated during processing and occurring errors will be passed to it to be visible in the task manager screen.
        Parameters:
        process - process to export
        inZielVerzeichnis - work directory of the user who triggered the export
        exportDmsTask - ExportDmsTask object to submit progress updates and errors
        Returns:
        false if an error condition was caught, true otherwise
